{"title":"太阳·月亮〔外一首〕","authors":["左夫"],"dates":[{"year":1988,"month":11,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳·月亮〔外一首〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"左夫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海角　天涯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这边有个太阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那边有个月亮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两颗圆圆的砝码"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地平线"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弧形的杠杆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桅樯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"塔状的支架"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳镀金"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月亮镀银"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个灿烂、素雅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个腼腆、豁达"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳　月亮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轮番升起落下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千百年彼此相望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怀着深深的牵挂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳　月亮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两颗圆圆的砝码"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁轻　谁重"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大海无法回答"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小船，爱的眼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江面有只孤独的小船"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烟雨迷蒙中时隐时现"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"船主哪儿去了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为何要解缆，不让它靠岸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小船是一片相思叶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是一瓣飘零的花瓣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不，不，小船是爱的眼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它的热盼急切切"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼帘忽闪忽闪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它的爱沉甸甸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泪水决了心湖的防线"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果它失望了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也许会一改初衷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"随江水漂得很远很远"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快用我们共同的思念"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快用我们共同的情感"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拖回那只孤独的小船"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泊在我们的心坎"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}